            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm h-100">
                    <div class="rounded-top" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745, #17a2b8);height:160px;">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center h-100">
                            <i class="bi bi-book" style="font-size:3rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <span class="badge bg-success mb-2">Research</span>
                        <h6 class="fw-bold">Qualitative vs Quantitative Research: When to Use Each</h6>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">Understand the differences between research methodologies and choose the right approach for your study.</p>
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                            <small class="text-muted"><i class="bi bi-calendar me-1"></i> May 5, 2026</small>
                            <small class="text-muted"><i class="bi bi-clock me-1"></i> 8 min</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-4">
            <p class="text-muted">More articles coming soon. Stay tuned for academic insights and tips!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>